arStrings.szText: Elias bound me and this demon as one. We are part of each other now.
Strained, since chains are around her. But she's coming to a realization now. The more she fights against Andariel, the worse it gets. Projected, said during combat
... I can control how tight the chains are!

Strained, since chains are around her. But she's coming to a realization now. The more she fights against Andariel, the worse it gets. Said to yourself as you come to the realization, but still projected as it is said during combat.
